ne-height:2;\"><b>小贴士</b></span> \r\n	</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>购买时不宜多，以免搁放几天后，大量的维生素C被破坏，减少菜品本身应具有的营养成分。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;\">菜谱推荐c菜谱推荐制作工艺</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;\"><strong>包菜炒腊肉</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div id=\"name22\" class=\"div\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:20px auto 0px;font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<div class=\"div\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:20px auto 0px;\">\r\n		<div class=\"cplist\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:10px auto;\">\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>\r\n					<div class=\"spImgJieshao\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 0px 4px;\">\r\n						<div style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;\">\r\n							<strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\">做法：</span></strong>&nbsp;\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;\">\r\n							<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>1、包菜洗净、切块；青蒜切段；红尖椒切块。&nbsp;</strong></span> \r\n						</div>\r\n						<div style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;\">\r\n							<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>2、包菜和腊肉分别用沸水焯一下。</strong></span> \r\n						</div>\r\n						<div style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;\">\r\n							<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>3、锅内放少许色拉油，下入腊肉炒香，加适量盐、味精、豆豉，放入包菜和青蒜翻炒数下，起锅装盘，摆上红尖椒做装饰即成。</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;text-align:center;\">\r\n							<img src=\"http://www.justeasy.com.cn/img/upload/20120106/15_171325_1.jpg\" width=\"344\" height=\"381\" title=\"www.buyfer.com 百惠臻品\" alt=\"www.buyfer.com 百惠臻品\" /><br />\r\n						</div>\r\n						<div class=\"clear\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:0px;\">\r\n						</div>\r\n					</div>\