\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;color:#E53333;font-size:18px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\">商品特色</span></span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\">十字花科芸薹属芸薹种白菜亚种的一个变种，一二年生草本植物，原产于中国的南方，以广东栽培较多。过去大多以采收长成大棵的植株上市，近年来餐馆业却盛行以棵菜烹饪，很受消费者欢迎，</span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\">秋冬季节空气特别干燥，寒风对人的皮肤伤害极大。白菜中含有丰富的维生素C、维生素E，多吃白菜，可以起到很好的护肤和养颜效果</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\">美味连连看</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#006600;\"> </span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<h1 class=\"g-page-title\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;\">大白菜鲜虾魔芋煲</span></strong> \r\n</h1>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';\"><strong><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:16px;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\">用料：</span></span></strong><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">大白菜 &nbsp; &nbsp; 魔芋 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>鲜虾 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;猪瘦肉 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">葱 &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; 姜 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></strong></span><span style=\"color:#006600;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#009900;\">生抽</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#009900;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#E56600;\"><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:16px;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\">做法：</span><span style=\"line-height:2;color:#009900;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">1.&nbsp;大白菜切段儿，魔芋切块儿，猪瘦肉切薄片。&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">2.&nbsp;砂锅内倒入适量水，煮沸烧开后，倒入适量生抽，同时放入切好的葱姜。&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">3.&nbsp;锅内的汤再次沸腾之后，放入猪肉片及魔芋块儿。&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">4.&nbsp;汤再次烧开后，放入鲜虾。&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">5.&nbsp;鲜虾变红后汤烧开后，撇去浮沫，然后放入大白菜。</span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">6.&nbsp;汤再次沸腾之后，放入盐调味，白菜煮熟之后，就可出锅。&nbsp;</span></span><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#E56600;font-size:16px;\"> \r\n<h2 class=\"g-sub-title\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">小贴士</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<div class=\"g-recipe-tips g-f14\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">1. 各种材料放入的次序很重要，每放完一种食材之后，都要等锅内的汤再次沸腾之后，再放入下一种食材。&nbsp;</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"g-recipe-tips g-f14\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">2. 放入白菜后千万不可以盖上锅盖，否则白菜就不能保持绿色，会变黄</span> \r\n</div>\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span>', '', '37', '0', '1', '1', '1', '大白菜秧子|百惠臻品', '大白菜秧子 百惠臻品源自大自然的味道。');
