\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\">6.降血糖</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n	<p style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\">适宜人群</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<b><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">【</span><span style=\"color:#E53333;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">宜】</span></b> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">一般人群均可食用；</span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">热病患者、肥胖、高血压、高血脂、水肿、癌症、嗜酒者多食；</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">是糖尿病人首选的食品之一；</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<b><span style=\"color:#E53333;line-height:2;\">【禁】</span></b> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">脾胃虚弱、腹痛腹泻、肺寒咳嗽者都应少吃，因黄瓜性凉，胃寒患者食之易致腹痛泄泻。</span> \r\n	</div>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<br />\r\n	</p>\r\n<span style=\"font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-weight:bold;\"> \r\n	<h3>\r\n		<span style=\"color:#006600;font-size:14px;\"></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;\">美味连连看</span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<br />\r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		黄瓜木耳炒鸡蛋\r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><img border=\"0\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.justeasy.com.cn/img/upload/20121123/1012720_2.jpg\" style=\"height:auto;width:auto;\" /></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\">1，黄瓜洗净，切片。木耳泡发，去蒂，洗净&nbsp;</span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\">2.&nbsp; 鸡蛋打入碗内，这个时候关键的步骤来了，在鸡蛋里面加一点点料酒、水、一点点盐，然后顺着一个方向将鸡蛋搅匀，</span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\">这样搅出来的鸡蛋口感更好</span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\">3，热锅热油倒入打好的蛋液翻炒，稍微成型之后快速盛出</span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\">4，再次热锅倒油，葱花儿爆锅，放木耳进去翻炒，之后放鸡蛋，最后放切好的黄瓜</span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\">5，出锅之前放盐，因为之前蛋液里面放过一点了，所以要比平时炒菜时稍微少一点</span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">6，起锅，装盘</span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"color:#006600;font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;line-height:20px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\">温馨小提示</span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<p>\r\n		<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n	</p>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\">1，搅蛋液的时候加料酒和水，可以去除鸡蛋的腥味，而且会让炒出的鸡蛋更蓬松一点，口感更好。</span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:small;color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:16px;\"> <span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\">2，鸡蛋成型之后一定要快速盛出，因为后面还要二次入锅，鸡蛋老了不好吃。</span></span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n	<h3 style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\">\r\n		<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-size:small;\"><span style=\"color:#006600;font-size:16px;\"> <span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\">3，</span><span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;\">放盐的时候，因为之前蛋液里面放过一点了，所以要比平时炒菜时稍微少一点。</span></span></span></span> \r\n	</h3>\r\n</span></span><span></span> \r\n</h2>', '', '37', '0', '1', '1', '1', '黄瓜|百惠臻品', '黄瓜 百惠臻品源自大自然的味道。');
