erdana, Tahoma, 宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:\'Microsoft YaHei\';color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>红<strong>菜</strong>椒含有丰富的维生素C</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>和胡萝卜素</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>(维生素A前体)。但在黄色<strong>菜</strong>椒和尤其是绿色<strong>菜</strong>椒（基本为未成熟果</strong></span></span><span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>实）中这两种维生素含量则相对显著偏低。此外，辣椒还富含多种的维生素B6</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>（尤其是维生素</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>)，以及钾，镁和铁等人体所必需微量元素。<strong>菜</strong>椒中高含量的维生素C还有助于食物，比如豆类和谷物，中非血红素</strong></span><span><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><strong>源的铁元素的吸收</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;color:#009900;\"><strong>，</strong></span></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>红<strong>菜</strong>椒带有辛香味,能去除菜肴中的腥味,营养价值甚高，除了含有丰富的胡萝卜素外,一根红<strong>菜</strong>椒还大约含有5000个国际单位的维生素A,可满足成年人的每天需求量,此外还含有超过100毫克的维生素C。这些丰富的抗氧化剂,能中和体内的有害氧分子自由基,有益于人体健康。长期摄取红<strong>菜</strong>椒,还有抗衰老的作用</strong></span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>食疗作用</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;\">\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>1、健胃助消化2、</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>预防胆结石&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>3、改善心脏功能 &nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>4、降血糖 &nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>5、缓解皮肤疼痛 &nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>6、减肥作用</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:28px;color:#e53333;font-size:18px;\"><strong>适用人群</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span style=\"line-height:28px;color:#e53333;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【宜】</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:28px;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>一般人群均可食用</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#e53333;font-size:14px;\">【忌】</span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:24px;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>阴虚有热者勿食；因红辣椒具有较强的刺激性，容易引起口干、咳嗽、咽痛、</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:28px;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>便秘</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:24px;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>等。同时眼疾患者、食管炎、胃肠炎、</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:28px;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>胃</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:28px;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>溃疡</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:24px;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>、痔疮患者应少吃或忌食；另外除有火热病症或阴虚火旺外，</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:28px;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>高血压病</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:24px;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>，肺结核病患者</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:28px;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>以及</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:28px;font-family:Arial;color:#009900;font-size:16px;\"><strong>肠胃功能不佳者</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"background-color:#ffffff;font-family:Arial, Verdana, Tahoma, 宋体;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '51', '0', '1', '1', '1', '红菜椒|百惠臻品', '红菜椒 百惠臻品源自大自然的味道。');
