Sun;\"><strong>莴笋与黑木耳同食，对高血压、高血脂、糖尿病、心血管病有很好的预防和辅助治疗作用。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>莴笋与胡萝卜同食，不仅有利于营养吸收，而且还可以促消化。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>莴笋与蒜苗同炒可以预防和辅助治疗高血压。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>【</strong></span><span style=\"color:#E53333;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>忌</strong></span><span style=\"line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>】</strong></span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>莴笋与乳酪同食，容易导致消化不良，引起腹痛、腹泻。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>莴笋与石榴同食，易产生毒素。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />', '', '45', '0', '1', '1', '1', '莴笋|百惠臻品', '莴笋 百惠臻品源自大自然的味道。');
INSERT INTO `ot_goods` VALUES ('96', '2013-05-23 22:55:26', '2013-06-19 19:45:16', 'goods', '49', '0', '韭菜', '/500g', '3.98', '1111', '500g', '201306051847422323.jpg', 'a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"201306051847508415.jpg\";}', '', '2373', '<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E53333;line-height:2;\"><strong>商品详情</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>品名：韭菜</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>功效：</strong></span><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>1、</strong></span><strong><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">补肾</span></strong><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>温阳&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>2、益肝健胃&nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>3、行气理血 &nbsp;</strong></span><span style=\"background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>4、润肠通便</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-weight:bold;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:18px;background-color:#FFFFFF;font-family:Arial;font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">食疗偏方<img src=\"/upfiles/attached/image/20130605/20130605104806_18061.jpg\" width=\"565\" height=\"564\" title=\"www.buyfer.com 百惠臻品\" align=\"right\" alt=\"www.buyfer.com 百惠臻品\" /></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">现代研究证明，韭菜叶含硫化物、苷类和苦味质，有较多的胡萝卜素上族维生素、维生素C以及钙、磷、钾、铁等矿物质，食用或外用有广泛的保健功效。下面就是韭菜的药效妙用，仅供大家作为参考。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（1）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治</span></b><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\">白带</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">醋煮韭菜籽焙干研末，炼蜜为丸。空腹以酒送服，每次30丸(丸如梧桐子大)。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（2）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治血崩</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜250克，煮糯米酒服之。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（3）</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治子宫脱垂</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜250克。煎汤熏洗外阴部。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（4）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治产后血晕</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜(切)入瓶内，注热醋，以瓶口对鼻。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（5）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治孕吐</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜汁50毫升，生姜汁10毫升，加糖适量，凋服。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（6）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治鼻出血</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜捣汁1杯，夏日冷服，冬天温服；阴虚血热引起鼻衄，用鲜韭菜根洗净后捣烂堵鼻孔内。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（7）</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治翻胃</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜汁100克，牛乳一盏。上用生姜汁25克，和匀。温服。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（8）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治慢性便秘</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜有“绿色蔬菜之王”美称，含有丰富的纤维素，每100克韭菜含1.5克纤维素，能刺激肠道，增强肠蠕动，有利于粪便的形成，及时将体内过剩的营养物随粪便排出，有利于预防肠癌和防治习惯性便秘。另外，这些纤维还可以把消化道中的沙砾、头发、金属屑包裹起来，随大便排出，故有“洗肠草”之称。也可用韭菜根叶捣汁1杯，温开水加少许酒冲服。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（9）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治赤痢</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜一把去梢取汁，和酒l盅，名日“韭汁酒”，温服。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（10）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治痔疮</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜不以多少，先烧热汤，以盆盛汤在内，盆上用器具盖之，留一窍，却以韭菜于汤内泡之，以谷道坐窍上，令气蒸熏；候温，用韭菜轻轻洗疮数次。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">11）</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治脱肛不缩</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">生韭一斤。细切，以酥拌炒令熟，分为两处，以软帛裹，更互熨之，冷即再易，以入为度。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">12）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治胸痹</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">，心中急痛如锥刺，不得俯仰，自汗出，或痛彻背上，不治或至死：生韭或根五斤(洗)，捣汁。灌少许，即吐胸中恶血。(《孟诜方》)</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">13）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治阳虚肾冷</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">，阳道不振，或腰膝冷疼，遗精梦泄</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭菜白八两，胡桃肉(去皮)二两。同脂麻油炒熟，日食之，服一月。(《方脉正宗》)</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">14）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">止水谷痢</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭作羹粥，炸炒。任食之。(《食医心镜》)</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">15）</span></b><b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">治消渴引饮无度</span></b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">：</span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">韭苗日吃三、五两。或炒或作羹，无入盐，但吃得十斤即佳。过清明勿吃。(《政和本草》)</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E53333;line-height:2;\">食疗作用</span><span style=\"color:#009900;\"><span style=\"color:#E53333;line-height:2;\">&nbsp; </span><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E53333;\"><img src=\"/upfiles/attached/image/20130523/20130523152231_94572.jpg\" width=\"353\" height=\"265\" title=\"www.buyfer.com 百惠臻品\" align=\"right\" alt=\"www.buyfer.com 百惠臻品\" /></span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">1、增进食欲</span></b> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">2、健胃消食</span></b> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong> \r\n	<div class=\"para\">\r\n		<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">3、散瘀活血</span></b> \r\n	</div>\r\n</strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">4、杀菌消炎</span></b> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">5、护肤明目</span></b> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">6、补气壮阳</span></b> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">7、调经散寒</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<b><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><br />\r\n</span></b> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong> \r\n	<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-size:18px;\">\r\n		<span class=\"headline-content\" style=\"color:#E53333;line-height:2;\">适宜人群</span> \r\n	</h2>\r\n</strong> \r\n</h2>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">一般人群均能食用。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（1）适宜便秘、产后想断乳的女性、寒性体质等人群。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（2） 便秘者建议多吃，因为韭菜含有大量的膳食纤维，能改善肠道，润肠通便。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">（3）如果吃多的话，会导致轻微腹泻。</span> \r\n</div>\r\n<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;line-height:18px;color:#E53333;\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:normal;line-height:18px;color:#E53333;\"><strong>小贴士</strong></span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;\"><strong>【</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:18px;\"><strong>忌</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;\"><strong>】</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+菠菜】同食会有滑肠作用，容易引起腹泻。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+牛肉】发热动火，引起牙齿肿痛，口疮。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+白酒】引起胃炎，胃溃肠病复发。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+蜂蜜】同食容易引起腹泻。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+牛奶】因韭菜含大量草酸，与牛奶同吃，会形成不易溶解的草酸钙，阻碍肠道对钙质的吸收。</strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;\">【</span><span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#009900;\"><strong>宜</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;\">】</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+绿豆芽】下气，通便。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+蘑菇】通便解毒，提高免疫力。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+豆腐、鸡蛋】益气养颜，健胃提神。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+鲫鱼】润肠止泻。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+虾】补肾、壮阳、固精。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+猪肝】杀菌、助消化、促进营养素吸收。</strong></span><br />\r\n<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;\"><strong>【韭菜+鸡蛋】两者同食补益作用明显，对胃病和肾病患者有很大的作用。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</h2>\r\n<b></b> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<b></b><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '67', '0', '1,2,4,6', '1', '1', '韭菜|百惠臻品', '韭菜 百惠臻品源自大自然的味道。');
INSERT INTO `ot_goods` VALUES ('100', '2013-05-24 22:26:51', '2013-06-14 09:01:33', 'goods', '51', '0', '茭白', '/500g', '4.98', '1215', '400-500g', '201306131251014134.jpg', 'a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"201306131251148877.jpg\";}', '41,72', '2393', '<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E53333;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;\">商品详情<img src=\"/upfiles/attached/image/20130613/20130613045143_20417.jpg\" width=\"497\" height=\"394\" title=\"www.buyfer.com\" align=\"right\" alt=\"www.buyfer.com\" /></span></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>品名：</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>茭白</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>功效：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:2;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#009900;\"><strong>清热止渴.利尿除湿。</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><span style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"line-height:2;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;line-height:2;color:#E53333;\"><strong>食疗作用</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:24px;\"> </span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<strong><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\">1. 利尿止渴、解酒毒：</span></strong> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>茭白甘寒，性滑而利，既能利尿祛水，辅助治疗四肢浮肿、小便不利等症，又能清暑解烦而止渴，夏季食用尤为适宜，可清热通便，除烦解酒，还能解除酒毒，治酒醉不醒。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>2. 补虚健体</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>茭白含较多的碳水化合物、蛋白质、脂肪等，能补充人体的营养物质，具有健壮机体的作用。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>3. 茭白能退黄疸，对于黄疸型肝炎有益。</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>用于催乳：茭白30克，通草10克，炖猪脚吃。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>4. 减肥美容</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span class=\"headline-content\" style=\"color:#E53333;line-height:1;\">适用人群</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span class=\"headline-content\" style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>【宜】</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>1、一般人群均可食用</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>2、更适宜高血压病人、黄胆肝炎患者、产后乳汁缺少的妇女、饮酒过量、酒精中毒的患者。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>【忌】</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>不适宜阳痿、遗精者、脾虚胃寒、肾脏疾病、尿路结石或尿中草酸盐类结晶较多者、腹泻者.</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#E53333;line-height:1;font-size:18px;font-family:NSimSun;\"><strong>相关菜谱</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 class=\"headline-2\" style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:Arial;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span class=\"headline-content\" style=\"color:#009900;line-height:1;\"><strong>茭白炒肉片</strong></span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#006600;line-height:2;\"><strong><span style=\"color:#009900;\">【原料】：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color:#009900;\">茭白3根、里脊肉150克、葱2根、辣椒1个、蒜末1小匙</span></strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>【调味料】：</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>A. 酒1大匙、酱油1大匙、淀粉1茶匙</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>B. 酱油1大匙、盐1/2茶匙、糖1茶匙、清水5大匙、水淀粉1/2大匙</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>【制作】：</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>1.里脊肉切片，拌入调味料A略腌；茭白去皮、洗净、切片；葱切小段；辣椒去籽、切片。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>2.先将肉片过油，再用2大匙油炒蒜末和茭白，然后肉片回锅，加入调味料B炒入味。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>3.放入葱段、辣椒，炒匀即盛出。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:24px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', '', '75', '0', '1,5', '1', '1', '茭白|百惠臻品', '茭白 百惠臻品源自大自然的味道');
INSERT INTO `ot_goods` VALUES ('97', '2013-05-24 11:16:56', '2013-06-14 14:12:37', 'goods', '49', '0', '生菜', '', '0.01', '1112', '', '201305241117174062.jpg', 'a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"201305241117586665.jpg\";}', '', '2378', '<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E53333;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;\">商品详情</span><img src=\"/upfiles/attached/image/20130524/20130524034313_38671.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"right\" height=\"500\" width=\"500\" /></strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#006600;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\">品名：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>生菜</strong></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>功效：</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#009900;\"><strong>镇痛催眠、降低胆固醇、辅助治疗神经衰弱、利尿、促进血液循环、抗病毒</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h2 class=\"headline-1\" style=\"font-size:18px;font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span class=\"headline-content\" style=\"color:#E53333;line-height:1;\">食疗作用</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>我们在做</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>凉菜</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>的时候，很多人都会想到生菜。生菜是最合适生吃的蔬菜。生菜含有丰富的营养成分，其纤维和维生素C比白菜多。生菜除生吃、清炒外，还能与蒜蓉、蚝油、</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>豆腐</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>、菌菇同炒，不同的搭配，生菜所发挥的功效是不一样的。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\"><strong>蒜蓉生菜</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>：</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>除了具有清炒生菜的功效</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>外，还</strong></span><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>有</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;\"></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>杀菌</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>、消炎和降血糖</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>的作用，甚至还可以</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>补脑</strong></span><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>。生菜含有丰富的维生素，具有</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>防止牙龈出血</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>以及</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>维生素C缺乏</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>等功效。大蒜有解毒、行滞、健胃的功效，对脘腹冷痛、痢疾、泄泻、肺痨、百日咳、感冒、疟疾等症有一定的</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>食疗</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>作用。</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:14px;color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;line-height:2;\"><strong>蚝油生菜</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>：</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>蚝油不是油质，而是在加工蚝豉（又名牡砺）时，煮蚝豉剩下的汤，此汤经过滤浓缩后即为蚝油。它是一种含多种营养成分、味道鲜美的调味作料。因此，蚝油生菜除</strong></span><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>有</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>降血脂、降血压、降血糖、促进智力发育</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>以及</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>抗衰老</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>等功效</strong></span><span style=\"color:#E53333;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>外，</strong></span><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>还能</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>利尿、促进血液循环、抗病毒、预防与治疗心脏病及肝病</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>。</strong></span></span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>生菜与营养丰富的豆腐搭配</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>食用，则是一种</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>高蛋白、低脂肪、低胆固醇、多维生素的菜肴，</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>具有</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>清肝利胆，滋阴补肾，增白皮肤、减肥健美</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>的作用。</strong></span></span><span style=\"color:#006600;\"><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>对</strong></span><span style=\"color:#009900;font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><strong>目赤肿痛、肺热咳嗽、消渴、脾虚腹胀</strong></span><span style=\"font-family:NSimSun;font-size:14px;line-height:2;color:#009900;\"><strong>等也有一定的食疗作用;而菌菇含有丰富的易于人体吸收的蛋白质，并具有补脾益气、润燥化痰以及较强的滋补功效，与生菜搭配食用，对热咳、痰多、胸闷、吐泻等有一定的食疗作用。</strong></span></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E53333;line-height:1;\"><strong>小贴士</strong></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E53333;line-height:2;\"><strong>[宜]</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>生菜+兔肉=促进营养物质的消化和吸收</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>生菜+大蒜=清热解毒、提高人体免疫力</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>生菜+豆腐=排毒养颜</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"font-size:18px;color:#E53333;line-height:2;\"><strong>[忌]</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"para\" style=\"font-family:arial, 宋体, sans-serif;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\">\r\n	<span style=\"color:#009900;line-height:2;\"><strong>生菜+醋=降低营养价值</strong></span> \r\n</div>\r\n<span style=\"color:#006600;\"><strong></strong></span> \r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>', '', '69', '0', '1', '1', '0', '生菜|百惠臻品', '生菜 百惠臻品源自大自然的味道。');
